author: andreasmyth
msg: Added PhaseManager interface and register implementation as an extension with the bus - removed getInPhases/getOutPhases from Bus api.
Inject activation namespaces into loaded objects, so e.g. a concrete BindingFactory can register itself for these with the BindingFactoryManager).
Added @PostConstruct methods to SOAPBindingFactory and HTTPTransportFactory to do just that.
Use separate ResourceResolvers to resolve bus, extension manager (and activation namespaces).
